Fidelis Anosike na Rita Dominic gbara akwụkwọ n'Imo steeti n'ụbọchị 19 nke ọnwa Epreelụ 2022, mere ka ndị mmadụ na-achọsi ike ịma onye ọ bụ.
Agbamakwụkwọ ha na-ewu ewu n'ihi na Dominic bụ ome ejije Nollywood a ma ama, ma bụrụkwa onye ndị mmadụ hụrụ n'anya nke ukwuu.
Ịhụnanya a mere ka ndị mmadụ na-agba tọọchị na-achọ ịma onye ọ bụzị nwunye ya si taa gawa n'ihu.
Ebe foto si, Fidelis Anosike
Ọ bụ onye hibere otu a kpọrọ Folio Media Group, nke nwezị ụlọntaakụkọ Daily Times Nigeria
Ọ bụ ya (ụlọọrụ ya) na-eme asọmpi Nwaanyị kacha mma na Naịjiria
Ọ gara mahadum na University of Benin, ebe ọ nọ gụọ Creativea and Applied Fine Arts
O mekwara OPM Program na mahadum Harvard Business School
Rita Dominic gbara ya n'anwụ dịka onye ọ na-ayị n'ọnwa Disemba afọ 2020
